author: Morgan Winsor
title: Coronavirus live updates: China lifts lockdown in Wuhan where global pandemic began
description: More than 1.4 million people around the world have been diagnosed with COVID-19 and over 82,000 of them have died since the virus emerged in China back in December.
content:
